WEBVTT

00:12:29.908 --> 00:12:32.041
They choose what works for them.

00:12:33.551 --> 00:12:35.773
So choice is everything.

00:12:35.797 --> 00:12:37.939
And power decides choice.

00:12:38.363 --> 00:12:41.609
And we need those in power --

00:12:41.633 --> 00:12:44.426
politicians, leaders, governments,

00:12:44.450 --> 00:12:47.651
architects, planners,
institutions, researchers --

00:12:47.675 --> 00:12:51.638
and all of us in our everyday lives
to respect choices.

00:12:52.857 --> 00:12:56.982
Instead of choosing what is right
for people, for the poor,

00:12:57.006 --> 00:12:59.939
let's acknowledge
and empower their choices.